      "text": "json vs XML\njson is fast in parsing\nbrowser has inbuilt json parsing engine \neasy to convert into binary \ntreated in object and array \nxml in string\ntransient keyword saves the serialization of the\ndata\nGrpc framework does serialization",
      "fontSize": 35.501650363080266,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "json vs XML\njson is fast in parsing\nbrowser has inbuilt json parsing engine \neasy to convert into binary \ntreated in object and array \nxml in string\ntransient keyword saves the serialization of the data\nGrpc framework does serialization",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
