      "text": "important note regarding recording \nyou can reacord via media recorder and convert stream into binary then \nbinary to RTMP using FFMPEG\n\n2) you can use webRTC to record then using media soup media server convert to rtmp \ncompatible  \n3) ffmpeg can convert to rtmp and choose where you want to throw it after converting into rtmp",
